{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "turn_index": 1, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:37:09.929182+00:00", "player_text": "你好", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "避难所内灯光昏黄，广播中仍传来断断续续的警报。你站在指挥台前，林振国正低头查看地图，神情凝重。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "你好，我是林振国，滨海市避难所的指挥官。现在情况紧急，外星入侵者已经切断了大部分通讯和能源供应。我们需要志愿者协助完成几项关键任务——你愿意帮忙吗？"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": "loc_001", "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}}, "memory_summary": "玩家首次与林振国对话，林振国介绍了当前局势并请求协助。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:world_bible:-:-:-:83573763", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:location:-:loc_001:-:3eaf5cf2", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:dcf6cdff"], "retrieved_ids": [], "filters": [{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 3, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 14}}}
{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "turn_index": 2, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:37:33.119132+00:00", "player_text": "我当然愿意帮忙", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "林振国抬起头，眼中闪过一丝欣慰，但很快又恢复了凝重。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "太好了，我们需要像你这样勇敢的人。目前有三个关键任务：苏婉婷工程师在废弃卫星站等你协助恢复通信；周小梅在红岩峡谷需要能源组件；青松镇的张晓雨则急需医疗物资。你可以选择先去哪边——但动作要快，外星人的巡逻队随时可能出现。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": "loc_001", "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}}, "memory_summary": "玩家表示愿意协助，林振国简要说明了三个支线任务及其地点，并让玩家自行选择优先目标。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:world_bible:-:-:-:83573763", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:location:-:loc_001:-:3eaf5cf2", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:dcf6cdff", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:b203fdf4", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:1:3c262559"], "retrieved_ids": [], "filters": [{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 5, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 15}}}
{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "turn_index": 3, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:37:57.370132+00:00", "player_text": "收到", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "林振国站在指挥台前，手指轻敲桌面，目光坚定地望向你。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "收到就好。记住，任务优先级由你决定，但别拖延太久——每一分钟都可能关系到更多人的生死。如果你需要补给，赵大勇在物资区；如果对路线有疑问，我可以给你简要说明。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}}, "memory_summary": "玩家确认接受任务，林振国提醒其尽快行动，并指出可向赵大勇获取补给或向自己咨询路线。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:world_bible:-:-:-:83573763", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:location:-:loc_001:-:3eaf5cf2", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:dcf6cdff", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:b203fdf4", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:2:039c2c9d", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:1:3c262559", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:2:fd1e2b5f"], "retrieved_ids": [], "filters": [{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 7, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 16}}}
{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "turn_index": 4, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:38:35.744451+00:00", "player_text": "听说你可以给我点补给，都有啥东西可以拿", "npc_id": "npc_003", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "物资区堆满了临时调配的箱子，赵大勇正忙着清点库存，额头上沁出细汗。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_003", "text": "哎呀，你来得正好！我是赵大勇，负责这儿的物资调配。现在能给你的不多，但有等离子电池两块、热能转换器一个，还有防护外壳碎片一块——都是从避难所仓库里翻出来的。你要去红岩峡谷的话，这些应该能帮上周小梅的忙。其他东西得你自己去任务地点找了，我这儿真没更多了！"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {"等离子电池": 2, "热能转换器": 1, "防护外壳碎片": 1}}, "memory_summary": "玩家向赵大勇索要补给，赵大勇提供了等离子电池x2、热能转换器x1和防护外壳碎片x1，这些物品被加入玩家库存。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:world_bible:-:-:-:83573763", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:location:-:loc_001:-:3eaf5cf2", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:npc_profile:npc_003:-:-:fa634498", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:1:3c262559", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:2:fd1e2b5f", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:3:95c43a1c"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:3:7b050b9f", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:2:039c2c9d", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:b203fdf4"], "filters": [{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "npc_id": "npc_003", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 6, "retrieved": 3, "store_total": 17}}}
