{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "turn_index": 10, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:40:52.901805+00:00", "player_text": "接下来我该干啥", "npc_id": "npc_002", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "苏婉婷将相位调制器小心地装入工具包，抬头看向你，眼神中透着一丝疲惫但坚定。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_002", "text": "太好了，通信系统终于能重启了！不过这只是开始——我们还得把外星信号数据传回避难所。接下来，我建议你去红岩峡谷找周小梅，她那边的‘峡谷能源’任务需要等离子电池、热能转换器和防护外壳碎片。你背包里好像已经有部分材料了？如果能帮她完成，就能拿到‘高能电容组’，那是主任务的关键组件之一。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}}, "memory_summary": "苏婉婷确认支线‘信号重启’已完成，并建议玩家前往红岩峡谷协助周小梅完成‘峡谷能源’任务，以获取高能电容组。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:world_bible:-:-:-:83573763", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:location:-:loc_001:-:3eaf5cf2", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:npc_profile:npc_002:-:-:3b000d2f", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_002:loc_001:5:b7e1e7ef", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_002:loc_001:6:909c288f", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_002:loc_001:7:e7ffbf8a", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_002:loc_001:8:e7ffbf8a", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_002:loc_001:9:99c5bc52", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:7:0b57b1b6", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:8:0b57b1b6", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:9:b974e1e5"], "retrieved_ids": [], "filters": [{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "npc_id": "npc_002", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 11, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 23}}}
