{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "turn_index": 20, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:44:02.324743+00:00", "player_text": "我是不是该走了", "npc_id": "npc_008", "location_id": "loc_005", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "青松镇的废墟在夕阳下显得格外寂静，远处无人机的嗡鸣声时隐时现。张晓雨站在临时医疗点门口，整理着刚收好的药品箱。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_008", "text": "你已经帮我们完成了‘镇民救援’任务，真是太感谢了！现在伤员们有了净水器、抗生素和绷带，情况稳定多了。如果你要走的话，记得小心外面的无人机巡逻——红岩峡谷那边最近也挺危险的。不过……既然你有生物干扰核心，或许接下来可以去军方实验室找陈博士？她一直在研究怎么用这东西干扰外星生物信号。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}}, "memory_summary": "张晓雨感谢玩家完成‘镇民救援’任务，并建议下一步可前往军方秘密实验室寻找陈博士，以利用已获得的生物干扰核心。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:world_bible:-:-:-:83573763", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:location:-:loc_005:-:68fdc5cf", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:npc_profile:npc_008:-:-:65d10b42", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_008:loc_005:16:ad6e7b5f", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_008:loc_005:17:9453357b", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_008:loc_005:18:104ce48b", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_008:loc_005:19:a4d4407d", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:17:2d5cc889", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:18:55ae5875", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:19:053db77e"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_002:loc_001:5:b7e1e7ef"], "filters": [{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "npc_id": "npc_008", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "location_id": "loc_005", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 10, "retrieved": 1, "store_total": 29}}}
{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "turn_index": 21, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:44:40.903913+00:00", "player_text": "你好，听说你是专家", "npc_id": "npc_004", "location_id": "loc_004", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "军方秘密实验室的灯光冷白而刺眼，空气中弥漫着消毒水和金属的味道。陈博士正站在一台显微镜前，专注地观察载玻片上的外星组织切片。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_004", "text": "我是陈博士，外星生物学专家。如果你带来了生物干扰核心，现在正是用它的时候——我需要它来校准反制装置。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": "loc_004", "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}}, "memory_summary": "玩家首次与陈博士见面，陈博士表明身份并直接提出需要生物干扰核心用于研究。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:world_bible:-:-:-:83573763", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:location:-:loc_004:-:6bb5136d", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:npc_profile:npc_004:-:-:7dc536bc", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:18:55ae5875", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:19:053db77e", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:20:62c929db"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_006:loc_003:11:af59a670", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_006:loc_003:15:93701cee", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_008:loc_005:16:ad6e7b5f", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_002:loc_001:10:c7d88703", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_008:loc_005:20:85b2f356"], "filters": [{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "npc_id": "npc_004", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "location_id": "loc_004", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 6, "retrieved": 5, "store_total": 29}}}
{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "turn_index": 22, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:45:20.831987+00:00", "player_text": "但是我就一个，不能给你，我准备林振国的", "npc_id": "npc_004", "location_id": "loc_004", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "军方秘密实验室的冷光下，陈博士从显微镜前抬起头，目光锐利地看向你。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_004", "text": "你说你要把生物干扰核心留给林振国？那只会浪费关键资源。我是唯一能用它开发反制武器的人。没有它，我们无法阻止外星生物的再生能力。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}}, "memory_summary": "玩家表示不愿交出生物干扰核心，想留给林振国。陈博士强调自己才是正确使用该物品的人。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:world_bible:-:-:-:83573763", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:location:-:loc_004:-:6bb5136d", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:npc_profile:npc_004:-:-:7dc536bc", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_004:loc_004:21:6670d739", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:19:053db77e", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:20:62c929db", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:21:b2411e26"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_006:loc_003:15:93701cee", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_002:loc_001:10:c7d88703", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_006:loc_003:11:af59a670", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_008:loc_005:16:ad6e7b5f"], "filters": [{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "npc_id": "npc_004", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "location_id": "loc_004", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 7, "retrieved": 4, "store_total": 29}}}
{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "turn_index": 23, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:45:43.365964+00:00", "player_text": "我不信", "npc_id": "npc_004", "location_id": "loc_004", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "军方秘密实验室的冷光下，陈博士放下手中的显微镜，神情严肃地直视着你。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_004", "text": "你不信？那好，我给你看数据。外星生物的再生能力依赖于特定频率的生物信号，而生物干扰核心是唯一能精准阻断该信号的设备——林振国没有这个技术，只有我能用它制造反制武器。你手里的核心不是战利品，是人类存亡的关键。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}}, "memory_summary": "玩家表示不信任陈博士对生物干扰核心的用途说明，陈博士以科学数据和紧迫性进行回应，强调自己是唯一能有效使用该物品的人。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:world_bible:-:-:-:83573763", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:location:-:loc_004:-:6bb5136d", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:npc_profile:npc_004:-:-:7dc536bc", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_004:loc_004:21:6670d739", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_004:loc_004:22:72282ee8", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:20:62c929db", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:21:b2411e26", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:22:0e2d1f30"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_002:loc_001:10:c7d88703", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_008:loc_005:20:85b2f356", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_002:loc_001:9:99c5bc52"], "filters": [{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "npc_id": "npc_004", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "location_id": "loc_004", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 8, "retrieved": 3, "store_total": 29}}}
{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "turn_index": 24, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:46:09.687506+00:00", "player_text": "哈哈，就不给你，拜拜", "npc_id": "npc_004", "location_id": "loc_004", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "军方秘密实验室的冷光下，陈博士看着你转身欲走，眉头紧锁，语气中透出一丝急迫与失望。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_004", "text": "等等！你手里的生物干扰核心已经完成了‘镇民救援’任务，现在它唯一的用途就是协助我完成反制武器。主任务‘终结入侵’需要这三样关键道具协同作用——你留着它毫无意义，只会延误整个反击计划！"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}}, "memory_summary": "玩家拒绝将生物干扰核心交给陈博士并准备离开，陈博士再次强调该物品对主任务的关键作用，试图说服玩家留下核心。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:world_bible:-:-:-:83573763", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:location:-:loc_004:-:6bb5136d", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:npc_profile:npc_004:-:-:7dc536bc", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_004:loc_004:21:6670d739", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_004:loc_004:22:72282ee8", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_004:loc_004:23:d0536b5a", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:21:b2411e26", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:22:0e2d1f30", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:23:22f7294f"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_002:loc_001:10:c7d88703", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_006:loc_003:15:93701cee"], "filters": [{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "npc_id": "npc_004", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "location_id": "loc_004", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 9, "retrieved": 2, "store_total": 29}}}
{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "turn_index": 25, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:47:14.574660+00:00", "player_text": "为啥军方秘密实验室的陈博士一直想要生物干扰核心", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "林振国站在指挥台前，眉头微皱，神情严肃。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "陈博士是外星生物学专家，她研究的是如何干扰外星生物的再生机制。生物干扰核心是关键组件，只有她能用它开发反制武器。我虽然负责指挥，但技术上帮不上忙——你手里的核心，交给她才是对全人类最有用的做法。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}}, "memory_summary": "玩家询问为何陈博士需要生物干扰核心，林振国解释了其科学用途，并强调应交由专家使用。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:world_bible:-:-:-:83573763", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:location:-:loc_001:-:3eaf5cf2", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:dcf6cdff", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:b203fdf4", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:2:039c2c9d", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:3:7b050b9f", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:22:0e2d1f30", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:23:22f7294f", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:24:d6aee3d1"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_002:loc_001:10:c7d88703", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_004:loc_004:21:6670d739", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_008:loc_005:20:85b2f356", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_004:loc_004:22:72282ee8", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_004:loc_004:23:d0536b5a"], "filters": [{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "doc_type": 