{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "turn_index": 26, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:47:36.797412+00:00", "player_text": "为啥军方秘密实验室的陈博士一直想要生物干扰核心", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "林振国站在指挥台前，眉头微皱，神情严肃。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "陈博士是外星生物学专家，她研究的是如何干扰外星生物的再生机制。生物干扰核心是关键组件，只有她能用它开发反制武器。我虽然负责指挥，但技术上帮不上忙——你手里的核心，交给她才是对全人类最有用的做法。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}}, "memory_summary": "玩家再次询问为何陈博士需要生物干扰核心，林振国重申其科学用途，并强调应交由专家使用。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:world_bible:-:-:-:83573763", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:location:-:loc_001:-:3eaf5cf2", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:dcf6cdff", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:b203fdf4", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:2:039c2c9d", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:3:7b050b9f", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:25:1ad6e3de", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:23:22f7294f", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:24:d6aee3d1", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:25:75736690"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_004:loc_004:21:6670d739", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_008:loc_005:20:85b2f356", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_004:loc_004:22:72282ee8", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_004:loc_004:23:d0536b5a"], "filters": [{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary"]}, {"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "doc_type":