{"session_id": "20260303_093526_46f0422c", "turn_index": 27, "timestamp": "2026-03-03T09:48:19.274720+00:00", "player_text": "好吧，但是我还是决定把东西给你，完成我的任务", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "林振国站在指挥台前，神情略显疲惫但目光坚定。他注意到你语气的转变，微微点头。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "很好，你做出了正确的选择。既然你已经集齐了相位调制器、高能电容组和生物干扰核心，主任务‘终结入侵’的条件就满足了。下一步，你应该立刻前往军方秘密实验室，把这三样关键道具交给陈博士——只有她能将它们整合成反制武器。时间紧迫，外星人不会给我们太多准备机会。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [{"quest_id": "quest_main_001", "title": null, "category": null, "status": "active", "objective": null, "guidance": "前往军方秘密实验室，将相位调制器、高能电容组和生物干扰核心交给陈博士以完成反击准备。", "giver_npc_id": null, "reward_hint": null, "required_items": {}, "reward_items": {}, "collected_items_delta": {}}], "inventory_delta": {}}, "memory_summary": "玩家表示愿意交出物品以完成任务，林振国确认其已集齐主任务所需三件关键道具，并指示其前往军方秘密实验室交付给陈博士。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:world_bible:-:-:-:83573763", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:location:-:loc_001:-:3eaf5cf2", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:dcf6cdff", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:b203fdf4", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:2:039c2c9d", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:3:7b050b9f", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:25:1ad6e3de", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_001:loc_001:26:3221126a", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:24:d6aee3d1", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:25:75736690", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:summary:-:-:26:eb2be608"], "retrieved_ids": ["20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_008:loc_005:20:85b2f356", "20260303_093526_46f0422c:memory:npc_006:loc_003:15:93701cee", 